{"tid":1142695,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【放工人士注意】天文台特別提示：雷雨區未來3小時襲港","createTime":"2019-05-07T08:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T09:14:55.000Z","uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8de2dd438ae8636ca46517f5b7e89c25da23da81","tid":1142695,"uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"下班人士要留意，香港正受到「風雷雨」威脅！天文台下午4時10分發出特別天氣提示，指位於珠江口附近的雷雨區，會在未來兩三小時影響本港，呼籲市民應提高警惕。<br />\n<br />\n由於雷雨影響本港時適值香港下班交通繁忙時段，道路交通或受雨勢影響，市民下班回家時間或受阻延，宜留意路面交通最新情況。<br />\n<br />\n此外，天文台在4時05分發出雷暴警告，有效期至下午6時；同時預料高達每小時70公里或以上的陣風吹襲香港，而強烈季候風信號亦正生效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/326170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F326170&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HPuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=ce97edb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/326170</a><br />\n<br />\n放工先黎落雨<br />\n唔通個天都唔想我放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0267ca64781b6151b65f81a0c9758b4b679a9fd9","tid":1142695,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"不"},{"pid":"859c4f1e8a617c58de120daeb0c5f8fee2241d15","tid":1142695,"uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:52:50.000Z","msg":"仲要唔記得帶遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db148d73cd71c5a0dc4442cdd0761127e5a0e9bd","tid":1142695,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e22788e0283b4d035ec72f06b5abe823e26ffea0","tid":1142695,"uid":157487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"Fuck"},{"pid":"d578318107b407c12fe66985cc3d4cbb82ec4847","tid":1142695,"uid":249088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T08:56:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}